{"tid":798336,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"隔牆有耳： 黃子悅成功拎匙入宿　 多謝吳思諾 - 李八方","createTime":"2018-08-29T08:31:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T08:31:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ea56cffd99d929933537e763508000c417d01316","tid":798336,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T08:31:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180829/20487049\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180829%2F20487049&d=Y6%2BhmZRuZm2cBO01iDldpgIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=d08fadcc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180829%2F20487049&h=384c71c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180829/20487049</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年08月29日 <br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：<br />\n黃子悅成功拎匙入宿　<br />\n多謝吳思諾 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180829/large/a1306a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180829%2Flarge%2Fa1306a.gif&h=fc8956bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃子悅拎住宿舍鎖匙自拍，開心些牙。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嶺南大學學生、前學民思潮成員黃子悅早前質疑嶺大宿舍政策涉歧視情緒病患，話自己去年因情緒問題休學一年及退宿，求醫後病情改善，醫生都證明適合復課，但嶺大舍堂要求佢提供病歷，黃子悅話病歷屬私隱，唔明白點解要提供自己嘅病歷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180829/large/29ls5p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180829%2Flarge%2F29ls5p3.jpg&h=a57357ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吳思諾<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n病歷風波　校方開會探討<br />\n<br />\n事件隔咗十幾日，終於有曙光，黃子悅噚日喺facebook公佈，佢終於成功入宿，攞到「林護堂」嘅鎖匙：「終於終於拎到房匙了！！！！嗚，好感動 ，原來有得入宿係咁幸福嘅事&hellip;&hellip;校內平機會9月頭會就相關事宜／學校政策開會探討，詳情我仲問緊。」佢仲拎住條鎖匙，開開心心自拍咗張相上載分享。<br />\n<br />\n黃子悅喺留言中特別鳴謝咗一大班朋友，唔少都係嶺大嘅同學仔，比較特別嘅係佢同時鳴謝來自民主黨嘅靚女大律師吳思諾（Senia），唔通今次Senia有份幫手？八方有搵Senia問佢內情，但佢到截稿仍未有回覆。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n隔牆有耳： 90後空姐空少接棒　 撐起港龍工會 (李八方)"}]}